#. Tag: title
#: storage_filesystems.xml:2243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Large file support in Linux"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_filesystems.xml:2245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Originally, Linux supported a maximum file size of 2&nbsp;GiB (2 "
"<superscript>31</superscript> bytes). Unless a file system comes with large "
"file support, the maximum file size on a 32-bit system is 2 GiB."
