#. Tag: para
#: storage_filesystems.xml:2530
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Approximately 1024. The actual number depends on the length of the device "
"number strings for each multipath device. It is a compile-time variable "
"within multipath-tools, which can be raised if this limit poses a problem."
